replies.body:
It's not a specific source, it's more like a collection of vague tidbits that add up, including internal chat with some of the player support guys we have in the volunteer Discord (though there was a support ticket that more clearly stated this was the case, and I never saved it). Like you said;

> Most the time, there isn't a set number, cos Riot wants you to fully reform instead of faking it for a set number of games.

Even if you got Tantram to answer you directly I don't think you're getting more than that. It's not worth pursuing imo, just encourage players to focus on reforming.
